event_details.name: Trek Through the Hidden Temple
event_details.description: There's treasure in this here Temple, if you're brave and adventurous enough to seek it out! Collect Torches and reset the world to start the Trek Through the Hidden Temple objectives and recruit new Crusaders!

details.shop_desc: Each Jeweled Hidden Temple Chest contains five cards; two are guaranteed to be gear for the four Event Crusaders (at least one of which will be rare or better). Also guarantees two random trinkets and one time warp card.

event_details.name: A Troublesome Temple
event_details.description: [Not Shown In Game For Mini Events]

details.shop_desc: Each Troublesome Jeweled Chest contains five cards, of which two are guaranteed to be equipment for Serpent King Draco, the Princess, Khouri the Witch Doctor, Montana James, or Prince Sal the Merman (at least one of which will be rare or better). Also guarantees two random trinkets and one time warp card.
details.promo_buff_desc: The new event can be challenging if it's your first time through. Use these special weekend buffs to power through and unlock those tier 2 objectives!
details.promo_chest_desc: Check out these limited-time Troublesome Chests that contain equipment for just the five Crusaders above! (Only for previously unlocked Crusaders)
